20:47.613 --> 20:49.748 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
your husband's legacy as
president.

20:49.782 --> 20:52.685 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
NANCY REAGAN: Well, he believed
in it strongly,
as did I.

20:52.718 --> 20:56.689 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Years later,
President Reagan
developed Alzheimer's, and the
first lady

