21:00.426 --> 21:05.331 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Did you feel you
had the chance
to say goodbye to him?

21:05.364 --> 21:15.107 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
NANCY REAGAN: Yes. As a matter
