lives.

24:33.138 --> 24:37.142 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And they were genuine requests:
Come up and
tell us about what you're doing,
what we should

24:37.176 --> 24:43.182 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
