direct participant.

25:05.204 --> 25:10.709 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL BESCHLOSS: And always
when she was
first lady and afterwards wanted
this idea

25:10.743 --> 25:16.181 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
