true. I think, as time goes on,
we will find

25:30.963 --> 25:32.731 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
that her role was very large.

25:32.765 --> 25:36.568 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: When you think
about, Michael,
in historical contact, the
previous two or

25:36.602 --> 25:41.106 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
three first ladies before her
and what kind
of a departure that was, maybe
even the tone

25:41.140 --> 25:42.941 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that it set for the country, it
was different.

25:42.975 --> 25:46.678 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL BESCHLOSS: It was,
although Rosalynn
Carter had attended Cabinet
meetings, got

25:46.712 --> 25:51.316 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
