25:51.350 --> 25:55.921 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But when you think about it,
Hari, in the
1980s, Nancy Reagan was
criticized in many

25:55.954 --> 26:03.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
