(LAUGHTER)

27:29.748 --> 27:33.018 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JAMES ROSEBUSH: And that drew a
lot of laughter.

27:33.051 --> 27:39.057 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
