my husband,

29:09.881 --> 29:12.050 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
not, how can I pursue an
ideological agenda?

29:12.084 --> 29:17.556 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: All right,
